author: The Critical Drinker
description:
Will The Running Man be a November hit, or another failed remake? Why is Ruby Rose going to war with Sydney Sweeney? And could Brie Larson be on the comeback trail with her new role in Mario Brothers 2? And why does Grace Randolph hate her? Join me, MauLer, Metatron, Nerdrotic and DarkHour as we find out.
